INTRODUCTION
A software application which is used to purchase tickets and buy/renew bus pass over the internet, 24hours throughout the day. Customers can register using manual/Google signup by verifying OTP sent on their mobile. Pass renewal can be done through webcam scanned QR code through QR scanner system.
Furthermore, customers do not need to pay in cash to buy bus pass or tickets because they can pay through various e-wallets. 
Bus pass system, to put it simply, system can provide pass identification using bar code/QR code, pass renewal, cancellation, updating, ticket purchasing etc.
	Registration using OTP verification.
	Purchasing pass for any route online post verification.
	Unique identification using QR codes on bus pass.
	Pass renewal through webcam scanned QR code.
	Ticket purchasing

Advantages
	Verification of the passengers can be done online using OTP. Though they have to first get their mobile number verified before registration.
	User can find all the bus pass related information online without going to the bus station.
	This online bus pass software system will help students and passengers get bus passes online and eliminate the need of standing in queues for passes or collecting a ticket for each journey.

Scope
This system can be used in any bus transport undertaking services. Using the system in government and private sectors, it can exclude the use of human efforts and saves lot of money and time.

Further aspects
	Payment through secured gateways can be implemented in future.
	Ticket availability can also be implemented.
 
IMPLEMENTATION
Hardware components
	Processor – Core i3
	Hard Disk – 500 MB
	Memory – 1GB
	Webcam

Software requirements
	Windows 7 or higher 
	Sql Server 2012
	Visual studio 2012
 
Tools used
	Python 3.4
	Google signup API
	QR code generator library
	QR code scanner library
	Python graphic library(pyQt)
	Sql Server 2012
	Python SQL driver(pyodbc, pymssql)
	SMS gateway
